  "name": "Daytime Tiger",
  "type": "spell",
  "img": "systems/n5eb/assets/Icons%20%26%20Images/Icons/Taijutsu.png",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>This jutsu can only be cast as a Taijutsu Finisher. As part of the requirements of this jutsu, you must have at least the \"Sixth Heavenly Breath: Gasp\" or the 7th Gate of Wonder of the 8 Inner Gates class feature active.</p><p>You take your palm and tap it with a closed fist creating a vortex of air pressure. Make a range Taijutsu attack. On a hit the target takes 10d12 bludgeoning and 10d12 force damage. Each creature within 30 feet around the target creature must make a Dexterity saving throw. A target takes 10d10 Force Damage on a failed save, or half on a successful one.</p>",
